            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Da Monte Maccaio a <placeName ref="#places/87">Suvereto</placeName>. In
                        nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Anni ab incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo vigesimo primo, mense martii, indictione Va Xa. Manifestus sum ego
                            <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/96">Ildibrandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> filius <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/97"
                            >Raineri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> et <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/98"
                            >Maximilla</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>, iugales, et filia <persName key="#Count"
                                ><name ref="Rogerius">Rugeri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comiti</rs>, et <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/99"
                            >Lupa</persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>, relicta <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#people/100">Malagalie</persName>, consentiente mihi prefato comite
                        Ildebrando, in mundio cuius volo permanere, quia per hanc cartula donationis
                        donamus et tradimus tibi, <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/103"
                            >Mauro</persName> venerabili <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> ex <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/78">Sancti
                            Quirici</orgName>, idest unus <rs key="#Mansi">mansus</rs> terre, quod
                        est in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi #Wine #Oil #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Count"
                            ref="#places/87">Monte Maccaio</placeName>, cum <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs> et <rs key="#Oil">oliveto</rs>, exceptis illis quae sunt
                            <orgName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/155">Sancti
                            Cipriani</orgName> et <orgName key="#Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68">Sancti Martini </orgName>et <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/86">Sancti
                            Gerboni</orgName> et <orgName key="#Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/78">Sancti Quirici</orgName>, et rectus fuit per
                            <persName key="#Mansi #Wine #Oil #Fiscal_property #Mention #Count"><name
                                ref="Benzo">Benzonem</name></persName>, et designatus est ab omni
                        parte, q[ui]a ex una parte est <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/79"
                            >Sancti Petri</orgName> de <placeName ref="#places/85"
                            key="#Monasteries">Monteviridi</placeName>, ex altera parte tenet
                            <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Viscount"
                            ref="#people/104">Rugerius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomes</rs>, desuper est terra <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/86">Sancti
                            Cerbonii</orgName>, desubtus via, quem autem mansum suprascriptum una
                        cum accessione et ingressione omnia in integrum sicut superius legitur
                        prefato Mauro abbati donamus atque tradimus, ut vos et ecclesia vestra et
                        successores vestri faciatis in(de) proprietario nomine iure quicquid
                        volueritis, sine omni nostra nostrorumque heredum contradictione. Eo tamen
                        tenore, si filii Malagalie <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> noluerint
                        confirmare, cum integram etatem habuerint, <rs key="#Offersio/donatio"
                            >cartula</rs> quam nos fecimus abbati Sancti Quirici de medietatem
                        omnium nostrarum terrarum, quam vos tenuistis ante unc diem in <placeName
                            ref="#places/89"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                            >Franciani</placeName> per <rs key="#Count">comitem</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/97">Rainerium</persName> et <rs
                            key="#Countess">comitissam</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/101">Adalasia</persName>, et medietatem de ipso <rs
                            key="#Castle">castellare</rs>, quam cartula si confirmaverunt, pacti
                        sumus cum Mauro abbate qui et cartula, cum suprascripto manso de Monte
                        Maccaiani, revertatur ad nos. Etiam promitto ego prefatus comes Ildebrandus
                        et comitissa Maximilla et comitissa Lupa, una cum nostris heredibus, tibi
                        Mauro abbati et tuis successoribus suprascripta nostram donatione defendere
                        ab omni homine, quod si facere non potuerimus aut si prefatum mansum vobis
                        tollere vel minuere voluerimus quovis ingenio, excepto si confirmatio facta
                        fuerit alterius cartule a filiis Malagalie, si prefata conditjo non
                        extiterit, promittimus nos una cum nostris heredibus tibi Mauro abbati et
                        tuis successoribus prefatum mansum restituere in duplum, sicut pro tempore
                        fuerit melioratus aut valuerit sub extimatione in consimili loco, quia inter
                        nos taliter convenimus. Actum in <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Fiscal_property #Residential #Castle #Count #Itinerary"
                            ref="#places/87">Suvereto</placeName>. Signa manuum prefati comitis et
                        comitissarum, qui que vero hanc cartula, qualiter supra legitur, scribere
                        rogaverunt. Signa manuum <persName key="#Witness #Viscount"
                            ref="#people/104">Rugerii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs> filii <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                                >Ildibrandi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Vulpellus">Vulpelli</name></persName> filii <persName><name
                                ref="Perlus">Perli</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Berardinus">B(er)ardini</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus/Crassus">Petri Grassi</name>
                        </persName>et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Malpilius"
                            >Malpilli</name></persName> filii eius et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Raineri</name></persName> filii <persName><name
                                ref="Rufinellus">Rufinelli</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Tancredus">Tancredi</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Huguccio">Ugiccionis</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Salarius">Salarii</name></persName>
                        filii <persName><name ref="Walfredus de Tremali">Valfredi</name></persName>
                        de <placeName>Tremali</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Wazo de Monte Liverenti">Vazonis</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Monte Liverenti</placeName>. Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Aimerigus"
                            >Aimerigus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domini
                        inperatoris post tradita complevi et dedi. </ab>
